column8: 1ON1 is a one on one SEO training service which offers individualized classes on search engine optimization through online and in person courses with a customized curriculum. The mission of 1ON1 is to offer search engine optimization training to entrepreneurs, small business owners, marketing professionals, website designers, and other individuals who have a website in a format that can allow them to directly apply lessons to their own businesses and learn based on their own needs and at their own pace.   1ON1 SEO training course was designed by Bruce Jones, an SEO tutor and industry expert who realized that there existed two main flaws with SEO that were inhibiting results. First, traditional SEO services offer optimizing websites as part of a digital marketing strategy. While these can work wonderfully, the client must continue to pay for search engine optimization, or else it will overtime become ineffective, since the client does not know how to keep up with the strategy after the optimization package is no longer being paid for. Second, those individuals that are wise to seek out an SEO teacher are offered group classes where they are taught at a fast pace about general information and are not given the chance to apply teachings to their own website.   Ultimately, your best investment when it comes to SEO is knowledge and a functioning skillset which will allow you to become your own expert. That is why the best SEO training course is one that gives you individual classes and works on your own website with you, based on your goals and needs.   Online Courses with your own SEO teacher  Our service offers a comprehensive one on one SEO training with an expert SEO tutor, who uses a virtual classroom to teach individual lessons that cater to your skillset and needs. Based on your existing knowledge, our SEO teacher will adapt a course on fundamental topics, from keyword research to optimized content writing to Google analytics and more. Classes are adapted based on the individual’s business goals, current website, and learning style so that learning and benefit from each class can be maximized.

column8: Eikonoklastes Therapeutics is developing a pipeline of disruptive new therapies that we can rapidly and relatively inexpensively advance from preclinical stage to clinical proof-of-concept and approval. We have now acquired our first two assets to treat devastating diseases that currently are severely inadequately treated. Our focus is on novel compounds that: 1) have platform capability where one molecule can treat multiple diseases with severe unmet clinical need, 2) will get preferred regulatory treatment due to the high unmet need and breakthrough potential, and 3) need relatively small clinical trials to achieve approval. Our 1st in class gene therapy (ET-101) has been engineered to overexpress Caveolin-1, which organizes & regulates synaptic receptors essential for neuromuscular signaling and function. It can treat a wide range of neurodegenerative diseases through precise, targeted overexpression of Caveolin-1 in neurons . We are also advancing a new generation of tissue factor (TF) therapies (ET-201) – therapeutics designed to target the cell surface receptor now known to be prevalent on solid tumor cells, tumor vasculature, and tumor stem cells, but absent on normal cells. By targeting these proteins which play a central role in the pathology of inflammation and angiogenesis, we can stop tumor growth, spread, and recurrence. Our first indications are neurodegenerative diseases and cancers with high unmet need and high mortality (e.g. ALS and triple negative breast cancer). A robust pipeline of additional indications (e.g. Alzheimer’s, Parkinson’s, etc. for ET-101; ovarian cancer, melanoma, etc. for ET-201) with severely inadequate treatment options will subsequently be pursued with these therapeutics.

column8: In today’s world, data is getting larger and complicated to analyze. Almost every company is gathering a lot of data and is looking for professionals who can analyze that data in order to make predictions & generate insights. Companies like Tencent are employing several thousands of data scientists who are using data and building machine learning models in order to generate predictions & make smarter decisions. Unfortunately, the demand for data scientist exceeds the supply. According to McKinsey research, there will be a shortage of 1.25 million data scientists by 2024. Quality data scientists are hard to find and expensive to employ as a single quality data scientist costs about $117,000 per year according to Glassdoor research. The data scientist has to then spend 45% of their time on model building that we believe is a very repetitive & time consuming process. On top of that, organizations that are thinking about building an in-house solution require more than 3.5 million RMB in investment & usually more than 6 months of development.  That is why we’re building mltrons, which is predictive analytics in 5 clicks. We’re are enabling organizations to build and leverage advanced machine learning & deep learning algorithms without ever writing a single line of code or worrying about investing in infrastructure. The users just need to prepare the data and upload it into the application after which they need to tell the system what they want to predict. Then automatically, our AI engine builds the best fit model for their problems and provides them with real-time predictions and insights.  Our AI engine is built on a robust architecture with state of the art algorithms. Our goal is to get companies from raw data to actionable predictions in the fastest way possible. Mltrons Ai engine can be connected to various data sources after which it loads the data, prepares and cleans the data, build hundreds of thousands of combinations of algorithms and then selects the best model for the problem that can be easily deployed in one click, either by using REST API, uploading new data or using our visual prediction. In essence, mltrons is simple yet scalable. But most importantly, mltrons is accurate & intelligent because as more data is fed it, it gets smarter.

column8: Our mission is enabling solutions for the global problem of substandard and falsified (SF) drugs.  The ARTiFACTS Verify SaaS platform contributes to reducing the incidence of Substandard and Falsified (SF) prescription pharmaceutical products in the supply chain by integrating systematic screening of the ingredients contained in medicines with chain-of-custody and secured provenance of all scientific and operational data:  • SF medicines are a $30 billion financial problem for stakeholders – in addition to the health and safety risks for patients and trustworthiness of the pharma supply chain;  • ARTiFACTS has completed a successful pilot with the University of Notre Dame which is deploying Verify in production use across its international network;  • We have invested $1.4 million in its development and are now seeking capital to support the commercial expansion of Verify.  Verify is a cloud-based information management system that provides fast, trusted and transparent targeted intelligence that regulatory authorities and other stakeholders rely on to remove SF products and their suppliers from the market. High-volume processing of medicine samples, accurate and trusted results for mitigation actions by stakeholder organizations are the primary benefits of Verify. Verify is unique in integrating scientific and operational supply chain data to address the global problem of SF drugs:  • Scientists and researchers use Verify as a distributed laboratory notebook to capture, analyze, secure and report data findings;  • Commercial and non-profit clients use Verify to detect, intervene and remove SF drugs from the market.

column8: Dogs get Lonely Without Furry Friends & New App Woofr Makes it Easy for Pooches to Connect and hopefully Help Their Humans Find Love Too! Experts agree that dogs are naturally pack animals, so even with a loving owner, they are often are missing something when not being able to be around fellow-four legged friends. The new app Woofr makes it easy for owners to link up and arrange doggie fun or even date days, love could be in the air for pooches and people alike! While a dog may be a man (or woman's) best friend, this still doesn't change the fact that their nature, as pack animals, is to want to spend time bonding with fellow canines. Did you know that there are over 500 million pet dogs globally, plus 1 in 5 has a social media account?!! Furthermore many people face the problem of not having access to another dog or dogs for their beloved pet to play and bond with, a solution was definitely needed. Answering the call, is what some are calling the “World's First Doggy Dating App” Woofr, a fun mobile app (‘social petwork’ if you will) that allows users to show off their pets to make connections with other local dog owners and arrange doggy play sessions, that will likely help their pets be more happy and healthy, and who knows, love could be on the cards for the owners too! The app is available for free on iOS and is coming soon on Android. So there may be just a bit of doggy romance or at least new friendships in the air for both hounds and humans. “When it comes to making connections swiping left or right has become an integral part of the dating experience for many people,” commented James Gaubert, from Woofr. “Now we've opened the door for pet people to use the same kind of cool and convenient technology to find BFF's for their beloved pooches, and maybe even a little love for themselves, something which everyone is sure to enjoy and appreciate, Woofr is the dating app that puts hounds first and humans second”. https://apple.co/2Kz1t0O

column8: PishPosh is the first app to crowdsource community service, like urban trash pickup, and reward those who participate. Here's how PishPosh works: users can download the app and log any work they serve in their area. Each minute of work earns them points, which they can redeem to enter giveaways, earn prizes, or, of course, convert to community service hours. The app also features a map that shows opportunity zones, allowing users to easily find areas in need of cleanup. With PishPosh, we aim to expand the scope of community service beyond just trash and clean-up. We envision a future where PishPosh can be used to crowdsource all types of community service, from organizing neighborhood events to volunteering at local charities or even, on a larger scale, supporting disaster relief. We have 2 goals for the next 24 months: reduce recidivism and beautify Californian communities. Jake Curreri founded PishPosh in Paris in October 2022. After spending 4 years at Nike with his first startup, SmallWorld, and gaining global recognition in digital health, he decided to re-focus fitness technology to better the future of our cities. PishPosh is headquartered in San Diego, California.

column8: The IINNTENNA is a next-generation antenna technology that is changing the global RF landscape and bringing telecommunications into the future. Our chief antenna scientist, Dr. Mohamed S. Sanad, changed the world’s telecommunications trajectory at Nokia in 1994, leading the invention of the first internally embedded mobile phone antennas. Hoping to change the problematic direction of antenna technology growing in size and weight without delivering more efficient signals, Dr. Sanad dedicated the past 15 years to create what we now know as the IINNTENNA- a smaller, cost effective, and monumentally more efficient antenna evolution. With decades of experience, a passion for revolutionary antenna advancement, and his innate concern for humanity at large, Dr. Sanad’s work has tackled even more problems than he initially intended to solve. This technology’s broadband, far-reaching capabilities are vast. In base station applications it eliminates the need for multiple towers in any given area, positively impacting the global landscape, minimizing deforestation, and significantly reducing exposure to radiation from the daily use of our wireless devices. In satellites the IINNTENNA immensely decreases the size and weight of the structure while maximizing efficiency, cost, functionality, and much more. The IINNTENNA’s features can be used with almost any technology, including all LTE, WiFi, and Bluetooth devices, which could lead to a positive chain reaction that will take us into a more health-conscious and environmentally friendly future for all technological advancement. With the wide-scale integration of this technology, we will also experience global impact with increased upload/download speeds, reduced SAR and PIM values in active antenna technologies, and worldwide connectivity extending to aircraft and space technology. Interested in learning more about how the next generation of antenna technology can be applied to your products and company? Contact us for a commitment-free consultation today.

column8: SDS produces a machine learning tool for the financial services industry which dramatically reduces the cost of harvesting and cleaning data.   The company was founded in 2018 by a team of analysts and investment professionals who had formerly worked as part of a development group in a San Francisco angel capital office.  Previously, the team had been tasked with building various in-house data solutions, including one to supply structured XBRL financials to subsidiary Revere Data (later acquired by FACTSET).  It was through this experience that the basis of SDS as a standalone provider was born.   The lightbulb moment for the team came when it moved beyond standard financials (Income Statement/Balance Sheet/Cash Flow) and began mining esoteric tables buried in 10K/Qs, such as REIT FFO (Funds From Operations) for a hedge fund manager client.  Although outside of the ordinary workflow, SDS tools easily accomplished the task with a skeleton crew of staff and a microscopic budget (compared to incumbent data purveyors).  At that point, the decision was made to commercialize. Since 2018, SDS has been in stealth mode, quietly improving its semantic parsing engine and its user interface, while preparing for a public launch.  We intend to disrupt a well established and very static industry which currently relies mostly on manual processes to populate databases.  Through automation, our platform improves the efficiency of collecting, maintaining, and updating financial information by an order of magnitude.   SDS anticipates an initial release in Fall of 2020.

column8: Luchismart is a cutting-edge cloud-based access control company that specializes in providing secure and intelligent solutions for modern businesses and organizations. With the aim of revolutionizing traditional access control systems, Luchismart combines advanced technology and innovative features to deliver a seamless and efficient access management experience. At the core of Luchismart's offerings is its robust cloud infrastructure, which enables organizations to manage access permissions and monitor activities remotely from anywhere in the world. By leveraging the power of the cloud, Luchismart eliminates the need for on-premises servers, simplifying the installation process and reducing maintenance costs. Luchismart offers a wide range of access control solutions tailored to meet the unique needs of various industries, including corporate offices, educational institutions, healthcare facilities, government agencies, and more. Whether it's securing entry points, managing visitor access, or restricting access to sensitive areas, Luchismart's scalable and customizable solutions provide comprehensive control over who can enter and exit premises. One of Luchismart's standout features is its intelligent access management system, which incorporates advanced analytics and machine learning algorithms. By analyzing access patterns and user behavior, Luchismart can detect anomalies and potential security threats in real-time, enabling proactive response and preventing unauthorized access attempts. With a user-friendly interface and intuitive controls, Luchismart ensures a seamless experience for both administrators and end-users. Administrators can easily configure access rules, set up schedules, and generate detailed reports, all from a centralized dashboard. Meanwhile, employees, visitors, or residents can conveniently access authorized areas using various credentials, such as keycards, mobile apps, or biometric authentication. Security is of utmost importance to Luchismart, and the company employs industry-leading encryption protocols and security measures to safeguard sensitive data and ensure privacy. Additionally, Luchismart is designed to integrate with other security systems, such as video surveillance, alarm systems, and intercoms, creating a comprehensive security ecosystem for complete peace of mind. In an era where flexibility, efficiency, and security are paramount, Luchismart stands as a trusted partner for organizations seeking advanced access control solutions. By harnessing the power of the cloud and incorporating intelligent features, Luchismart empowers businesses to enhance security, streamline operations, and embrace the future of access control management.

column8: Prophyles is reinventing Contact Management by pioneering a new category coined as Contacts-as-a-Service (CaaS).   Prophyles is solving the lingering problems in contact management related to data integrity, accuracy, synchronization, up-to-date, and privacy.  All current vendors, from low-end address books to high-end CRMs, use a centralized database which causes silos which are the main source of the problems.  Prophyles took a unique and contrarian approach by using a decentralized and distributed database in a peer-to-peer network in which profiles are connected using "Smart Contracts" in a blockchain - which is the core of our patent. Prophyles provides your entire digital footprint and those of your contacts, without ever compromising your or their privacy, and without ever being outdated since all Personal Information is constantly updated from the cloud onto your or their device, just like updates of mobile apps.
